    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The VANOS system has been proactively addressed, and the chassis remains rigid with a reinforced rear subframe. While the aesthetics reflect a dedicated driver's car, the powertrain is optimized for performance, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. An excellent candidate for an enthusiast looking for a visceral, analog machine with sorted internals.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
